description:
WILL SHIP FEB. 1ST.

WeWood plants a tree for every watch sold!

• 100% Natural Wood 

• Hypo-allergenic 

• Completely free of toxic chemicals 

• New Date Window

• Miyota movement 

• Adjustable to fit most any wrist

• Dimensions: 

Band: 8 3/4” (222 mm)

FACE (including wood frame / bezel): 1 1/2" (38 mm) Across, 1 1/2" (38mm) Long and 1/2" (12.75 mm) thick

Maple (BEIGE) 

The wood of this tree is often used in smoke houses and in culinary arts. It's also used to create many musical instruments like the violin and the guitar.
*Due to the season and age of the wood chosen for your unique WeWood Timepiece, colors may be darker or lighter (within reason and hue) than the photo.
